{"lang": "zh_TW", "eventid": "act22side", "eventName": "照我以火", "entryType": "ACTIVITY", "storyCode": "FC-1", "avgTag": "行動前", "storyName": "逃離與追逐", "storyInfo": "意圖避人耳目的葦草準備離開這些被當地巡邏隊追捕的塔拉流民。同時，追蹤深池動向的風笛和陳遇到了特殊的深池士兵。\n", "storyList": [{"id": 0, "prop": "HEADER", "attributes": {"key": "title_test", "is_skippable": "true", "fit_mode": "BLACK_MASK"}}, {"id": 1, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 2, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 3, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 4, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g2_reedmarshes", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 5, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 6, "prop": "PlayMusic", "attributes": {"key": "$normal_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 7, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 8, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 9, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 10, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 11, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 12, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 13, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別翻你那帳本了，還想著過幾天回去推上你的小車賣東西呢？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 14, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 15, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒有，不敢想，唉。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 16, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 17, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但是做了虧心事，我就總覺得要記下來。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 18, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 19, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生都是聰明人，受的是什麼傷，她看一眼就知道啦。既然她沒責怪你，那就是原諒你了。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 20, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 21, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可她說自己不是醫生，只是在賣藥的地方上班，學過一些急救知識，所以能指揮我們處理傷口......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 22, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 23, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你怎麼知道她說的是實話？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 24, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 25, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "要我說，她不是一般的醫生，但更不可能是什麼賣藥的。她帶的藥品種類那麼齊全，又出現在荒地上，多奇怪啊。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 26, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 27, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸對了，她手提箱裡都裝了什麼，你看清楚了嗎？你是做生意的，東西值多少錢，你心裡有數嗎？", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 28, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 29, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我沒仔細看。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 30, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 31, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你總不能連救命恩人的行李都想搶吧。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 32, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 33, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行了，我就是隨便問問。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 34, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 35, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉......你那裡還有麵包嗎？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 36, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_242", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 37, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒多少了。", "name": "塔拉流民"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_242"}, {"id": 38, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 39, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......還是分我一個吧，拜託了。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 40, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 41, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 42, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.2, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 43, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 44, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 45, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 46, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 47, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 48, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g2_reedmarshes", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 49, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 1.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 50, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 51, "prop": "musicvolume", "attributes": {"volume": 0.4, "fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 52, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 53, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 54, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 55, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 56, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "醫生。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 57, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 58, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "呃，不對，你不喜歡別人叫你醫生......那個，吃塊麵包嗎？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 59, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 60, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，謝謝。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 61, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 62, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你在看什麼？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 63, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 64, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "只是，一本古舊的塔拉詩歌集。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 65, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 66, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哦，哦，原來是塔拉語......我本來就不認識多少詞，寫出來的塔拉語我就更沒見過啦，哈哈。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1"}, {"id": 67, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 68, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你想坐在這裡的話，沒關係的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 69, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 70, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維恩", "content": " 好，呃..."}}, {"id": 71, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 72, "prop": "multiline", "attributes": {"name": "維恩", "end": "true", "content": " ...其實我就是想為昨晚的事情謝謝你。", "joined": " 好，呃... ...其實我就是想為昨晚的事情謝謝你。"}}, {"id": 73, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 74, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "可我只是給了一些藥。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 75, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 76, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......清洗傷口，包紮，那些事情，我該自己做的。只是，我還做不好。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#2$1"}, {"id": 77, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 78, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒事，那傷口我也不敢碰，確實嚇人。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}, {"id": 79, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 80, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......但我是想說，要不是你放了那把火，我們恐怕都脫不了身。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 81, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 82, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "火......？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#6$1"}, {"id": 83, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 84, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......不，火不是我放的，我只是路過。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#8$1"}, {"id": 85, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 86, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，既然你這麼說，那就當是巧合好啦。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 87, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 88, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唉，什麼深池，那些當兵的把不聽話的人都叫做深池。我們也就算了，你這樣的好心人，不該背上這麼重的罪名。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 89, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 90, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......你很憎恨深池？", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 91, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 92, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我......我說不上來。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#2$1"}, {"id": 93, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 94, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是從城裡來的，我還是給你提個醒吧。前段時間，深池的人來過這一帶。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 95, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 96, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "聽說他們跟維多利亞的一支軍隊撞上了，結果維多利亞人沒一個活下來。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 97, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 98, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "這件事把城裡的老爺們氣壞了，所以他們從特倫特郡調了一批當兵的出來，在石高原野上四處抓人，村子也燒了好幾座。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#1$1"}, {"id": 99, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 100, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......其實你真不該救我們，不值得。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 101, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 102, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 103, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 104, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我如果，不去在乎別人的生命，那我答應羅德島的事，就沒有做到......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#12$1"}, {"id": 105, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 106, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊？不好意思，你說話聲音實在太小了......", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 107, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 108, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，沒什麼......你剛剛說的情況，我知道一些，路上我會小心的。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 109, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 110, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸，你這就要走？", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 111, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 112, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯，天已經亮了，我不用你們指路了。", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#9$1"}, {"id": 113, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 114, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "好吧，好吧。我明白，像你這樣，把維多利亞語講得很標準的塔拉人，都不肯跟我們多說話。", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#6$1"}, {"id": 115, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 116, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 117, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 118, "prop": "playsound", "attributes": {"key": "$d_gen_walk_n"}}, {"id": 119, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1", "duration": 1.5}}, {"id": 120, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 121, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "喂，你們見到凱莉了嗎？差不多這麼高的女人，走路時尾巴搖搖晃晃的。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#8$1"}, {"id": 122, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 123, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "沒見到？那可以麻煩你在這附近找找嗎，醫生？她一晚上沒回來。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1"}, {"id": 124, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}}, {"id": 125, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "塞爾蒙，你的態度怎麼突然——", "name": "維恩"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_725_1#4$1"}, {"id": 126, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 127, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，維恩，你到我這邊來幫忙吧。", "name": "塞爾蒙"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_724_1#1$1"}, {"id": 128, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}}, {"id": 129, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "葦草"}, "figure_art": "avg_1020_reed2_1#1$1"}, {"id": 130, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 131, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 132, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 133, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 1.0}}, {"id": 134, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 135, "prop": "Background", "attributes": {"image": "34_g3_swamp_d", "screenadapt": "coverall"}}, {"id": 136, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 137, "prop": "playMusic", "attributes": {"intro": "$m_dia_street_intro", "key": "$m_dia_street_loop", "volume": 0.4}}, {"id": 138, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 139, "prop": "Delay", "attributes": {"time": 2.0}}, {"id": 140, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 141, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 142, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 143, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 144, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，這裡有信號？那是不是意味著我們又找錯方向了？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#3"}, {"id": 145, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 146, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "看起來是。這附近的通信設施沒被破壞，說明他們沒有朝這一帶前進。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 147, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 148, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "嗯......那羅德島有沒有說什麼？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 149, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 150, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和新聞裡說的沒什麼差別。昨晚有一小隊深池士兵在紅脊鎮放火，燒了駐軍處的一幢樓。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 151, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 152, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "但那隊士兵看起來還沒有逃到這片荒野上。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 153, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 154, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "剩下的都是無效資訊。近一個月，所有移動城市都恰好遠離這片荒地，外勤幹員沒有報告任何明顯的異常。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 155, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 156, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我們也只是見到了戰鬥留下的痕跡......從那些痕跡中，幾乎無法判斷戰鬥的規模。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 157, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 158, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "唯一能看出的是，交戰雙方的實力懸殊，那一隊維多利亞士兵幾乎是迅速戰敗。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 159, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#3$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 160, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......風笛，你在聽嗎？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#3$1"}, {"id": 161, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 162, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "欸？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#5"}, {"id": 163, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 164, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我看到你零件裝錯了方向，就知道你又走神了。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#6$1"}, {"id": 165, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 166, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "哇，陳陳，你居然連破城矛的結構都能看明白了！我當時可是學了好久才記住怎麼維護它。", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 167, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 168, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......結構我倒是沒有完全看懂。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 169, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 170, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "我剛剛在想，休斯為什麼在信裡說話總是像另一個人一樣，雖然這麼說好像沒什麼道理......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#7"}, {"id": 171, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 172, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "還好，我相信你一向直覺很準。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#8$1"}, {"id": 173, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 174, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "你是不是覺得他總有什麼話想說不敢說？", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 175, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 176, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......就好像我們上次去找過他之後，就有什麼人盯上他了一樣。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}, {"id": 177, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 178, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "對，就是這種感覺！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 179, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 180, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "那說明我們沒有走錯路。休斯給我們的消息是準確的，準確到引起了敵人的警覺。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 181, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 182, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "行軍路線可以隱藏，但戰備相關原材料的流向還是洩露了訊息。在過去幾個月內，被我們標記的幾支深池的部隊都在靠近這一帶。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#7$1"}, {"id": 183, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 184, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "特倫特郡外面的......無人區？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 185, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 186, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "......", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 187, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 188, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "陳陳，你怎麼突然警......", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 189, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 190, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "三點鐘方向。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 191, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 192, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 193, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 194, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "m", "name": "avg_npc_244", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "focus": "m", "duration": 0.7}}, {"id": 195, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.0}}, {"id": 196, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "——", "name": "深池士兵"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_244"}, {"id": 197, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 198, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 199, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 200, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 201, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "和小丘郡那個時候打扮一樣......是鬼魂部隊！", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#2"}, {"id": 202, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 203, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "快跟上——", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#1"}, {"id": 204, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 205, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "等等，風笛......他們看起來很奇怪。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 206, "prop": "dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 207, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 208, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "name": "avg_npc_244", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 209, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "bstart": 0.2, "bend": 0.7, "name": "avg_npc_244", "duration": 0.5}}, {"id": 210, "prop": "delay", "attributes": {"time": 1.5}}, {"id": 211, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"duration": 0.2, "isblock": "true"}}, {"id": 212, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 213, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "r", "name": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4", "focus": "r"}}, {"id": 214, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "啊，只有幾個人站在荒野上，像是站崗一樣......是誘餌嗎？", "name": "風笛"}, "figure_art": "avg_222_bpipe_1#4"}, {"id": 215, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 216, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "不，可能未必。他們讓我想起一些......在龍門發生的事。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 217, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {"slot": "l", "name": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1", "focus": "l"}}, {"id": 218, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": "別輕敵，我們慢慢靠近。", "name": "陳"}, "figure_art": "avg_npc_662_1#1$1"}, {"id": 219, "prop": "Dialog", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 220, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 0.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 0.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 221, "prop": "Blocker", "attributes": {"a": 1.0, "r": 0.0, "g": 0.0, "b": 0.0, "fadetime": 2.0, "block": "true"}}, {"id": 222, "prop": "stopmusic", "attributes": {"fadetime": 2.0}}, {"id": 223, "prop": "Character", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 224, "prop": "charslot", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 225, "prop": "Image", "attributes": {}}, {"id": 226, "prop": "name", "attributes": {"content": ""}}], "OPTIONTRACE": true}